reviewText:
An excellent instructional video with informative basics as well as great tying techniques that have helped improve the quality and appearance of my flies.
The content and tying techniques  has also helped me improve my Atlantic salmon tying techniques. I would recommend this video for anyone who wants to improve their tying skills on any type of flies with a focus on wet flies. There are techniques that are applicable to all styles of flies.
This is the primo video for everything you need for wet fly fishing. Every tyer and fly fishers needs this video!
